              ],
              "value": "14"
            },
            {
              "rowId": 74,
              "keyParts": [
                74,
                "p3",
                "verse",
                "v14",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "Then he threw himself on the neck of his brother Benjamin and wept, and Benjamin wept on his neck."
