              "keyParts": [
                "v014_NET_GEN_045",
                75,
                "p3",
                "verse",
                "v14",
                "plain_text"
              ],
              "value": "14 Then he threw himself on the neck of his brother Benjamin and wept, and Benjamin wept on his neck."
