                "v016_NET_GEN_045",
                85,
                "p4",
                "verse",
                "v16",
                "plain_text"
              ],
              "value": "16 Now it was reported in the household of Pharaoh, “Joseph’s brothers have arrived.” It pleased Pharaoh and his servants."
